'''NGC 1705'''是在[[繪架座|繪架座]]的一個[[特殊星系|特殊]][[透鏡星系|透鏡星系]]，與[[地球|地球]]的距離估計在1,700萬[[光年|光年]]<ref name="apod2003">{{citation
 | url = http://antwrp.gsfc.nasa.gov/apod/ap030423.html
 | publisher = Astronomy Picture of the Day
 | title = The Stars of NGC 1705
 | year = 2003
 | date = 2003-04-23
 | authors = Robert Nemiroff (MTU) & Jerry Bonnell (USRA)
 | accessdate = 2008-07-10
 | archive-date = 2008-05-22
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080522050629/http://antwrp.gsfc.nasa.gov/apod/ap030423.html
 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>，是[[劍魚座星系團|劍魚座星系團]]的一員<ref name="Huchraetal1982">{{citation
 | url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1982ApJ...257..423H
 | title = Groups of galaxies. I - Nearby groups
 | authors = Huchra, J. P.; Geller, M. J.
 | doi = 10.1086/160000
 | year = 1982
 | date = 1982-06-15
 | journal = Astrophysical Journal
 | issue = Part 1
 | volume = 257
 | pages = 423–437
 | accessdate = 2008-07-10
 | archive-date = 2018-10-23
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181023145745/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1982ApJ...257..423H
 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>。
這個星系是在1834年12月5日被[[約翰·弗里德里希·威廉·赫歇爾|約翰·弗里德里希·威廉·赫歇爾]]發現的。

